{"id":2642,"date":"2023-07-24T16:08:06","date_gmt":"2023-07-24T09:08:06","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2642"},"modified":"2023-09-18T16:09:52","modified_gmt":"2023-09-18T09:09:52","slug":"lop-cap-nhat-kien-thuc-chuyen-mon-duoc-thang-8","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/lop-cap-nhat-kien-thuc-chuyen-mon-duoc-thang-8\/","title":{"rendered":"L\u1edaP C\u1eacP NH\u1eacT KI\u1ebeN TH\u1ee8C CHUY\u00caN M\u00d4N D\u01af\u1ee2C TH\u00c1NG 8"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1edf c\u00e1c l\u1edbp \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o \u201cC\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n d\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d, h\u1ecdc online 100% t\u1ea1o thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i t\u1ed1i \u0111a cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m trong c\u00e1c c\u01a1 s\u1edf y t\u1ebf d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh kh\u00f3a \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh chung c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 Y t\u1ebf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sau khi tham gia \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o, h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p <\/span><b>\u201cGi\u1ea5y x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u1ec1 D\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u chu\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 Y T\u1ebf v\u1ec1 ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 h\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1 D\u01b0\u1ee3c.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o: <strong>8h00 \u0111\u1ebfn 17h30, Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt, 20\/08\/2023<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o: <strong>Tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u0103ng k\u00fd h\u1ecdc tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn: <strong>24\/07\/2023 \u0111\u1ebfn 19\/08\/2023; <\/strong><\/span><strong><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/forms.gle\/5eSa5sF723gVGzE98\">Form \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd <\/a><\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u1ed3 s\u01a1 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd bao g\u1ed3m:<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Th\u00f4ng tin c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 ng\u00e0nh D\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean quan;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u1ea2nh ch\u1ee5p ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 h\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u1ea2nh ch\u1ee5p b\u1eb1ng T\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p ng\u00e0nh d\u01b0\u1ee3c;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u1ea2nh ch\u1ee5p CMT\/CCCD.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-16927\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/CMD_Th8-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sau khi \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng kh\u00f3a h\u1ecdc, Nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd cung c\u1ea5p t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n h\u1ecdc tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn qua \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 Email tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y 19\/08\/2023. Do v\u1eady, h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd c\u1ea7n cung c\u1ea5p <b>ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Email v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i li\u00ean h\u1ec7.<\/b><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea5p Gi\u1ea5y x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn:<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Tham gia 80% th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111\u1ea1t 50%.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 c\u1ea5p gi\u1ea5y x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed kh\u00f3a h\u1ecdc:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> 600.000 \u0111\/h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean\/kh\u00f3a h\u1ecdc<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Xem th\u00eam n\u1ed9i dung chi ti\u1ebft kh\u00f3a h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/file\/d\/1FU9ml1CCkI9hYv7z_KxpaAzGcej_sQVg\/view?usp=drive_link\"><b><span style=\"color: #28469a;\">Th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n sinh c\u00e1c l\u1edbp C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u1ec1 D\u01b0\u1ee3c.<\/span><\/b><\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>Th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft\u00a0 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 theo \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9:<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b><i>Ph\u00f2ng \u0110\u00